ygData.msgSnippet: You can go to a dungeon, any dungeon in Kunark, then port to Emerald Jungle but thats not a real safe place for lower lvls.  Skyfire, but not a great place
ygData.messageBody:
You can go to a dungeon, any dungeon in Kunark, then port to Emerald Jungle
but thats not a real safe place for lower lvls. Skyfire, but not a great
place either with some luck and invis you could get to overthere faster.

Mu
